channel.description:
[size=14pt][b]Please Don't Post on this unless you want to join! Thanks :)[/b][/size]
About Me: Hi my name is Brian. I live in United States. I am almost 15 years old and I have always had an interest in programming. I am a little new to coding RSPS but i got the basics. I had my own server up called Arctic-Frost but it was too hard to run it myself. I had around 25 players and it was up for around 2 weeks. I was bad at advertising. It was a 317 server but I'm growing an interest in the newer 508+. I am starting a new server and I am probably going to use a 508 base. I would like to get server full screen. I am open to server base suggestions must be 508+. (full credits to respected owners) I would love to get together with some others and make a great server. Staff spots in game will be given to those who help. Programmers/coders will receive co-owner and others can receive admin/hidden admin. Lets make a great server!
Base [u][b]Idea[/b][/u]: Project Awesomeness 562 (davidscape base) credits laurent 248
